Works fine for now. It won't immediately ask for the registration information pending computer restart after installation. When you open the program, at the top there will be a button that says "Purchase Product" or something along those lines. Click that, type in name (all caps), copy the serial number, and paste it into the section. Don't worry about the hyphens, they will be taken out. Click register, and you're good. i suggest beginning musicians who are recording start out with something that is a bit more simple, such as Cool Edit Pro 2.1. Working torrent can be found here: http://thepiratebay.org/torrent/3802771/Cool_Edit_Pro_2.1_-_Full_working_and_registered.zip
